{"tid":2210070,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"魔鬼山現「立即啟動選舉」直幡","createTime":"2020-09-20T06:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T17:38:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":97,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5602017c885155c784862e147e63856a08dd0595","tid":2210070,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"今晨7時半，油塘魔鬼山出現一幅直幡，約20米長、1.5米闊，黑底白字寫上「立即啟動選舉」掛在崖石上。警方接報後聯絡消防處，至上午11時左右，消防員移除直幡。<br />\n<br />\n港府以疫情為由，透過《緊急法》押後原定本月6日舉行的立法會選舉，並由人大常委會決定現任議員延任一年。不過，有民間調查結果顯示，6成8受訪者認為應該重新舉行選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200920/2CIGEHDJ4RGENGV3BZD6IHXFRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200920%2F2CIGEHDJ4RGENGV3BZD6IHXFRQ%2F&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmmVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=ad3cf785\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200920%2F2CIGEHDJ4RGENGV3BZD6IHXFRQ%2F&h=c89eba9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200920/2CIGEHDJ4RGENGV3BZD6IHXFRQ/</a>"},{"pid":"729686212591345773b54b5ce767b5f913031fce","tid":2210070,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2fdd0a75dc3fe88aaf27ce0a970dc4388cbf5b","tid":2210070,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"729686212591345773b54b5ce767b5f913031fce","tid":2210070,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass